---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="RoomCalc - Material Estimator" description="8 construction calculators + shopping list. Tile, paint, wallpaper, concrete. Free forever, no ads, offline.">
  <div class="pt-24 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
      <a href="/en/apps" class="text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-accent-purple transition-colors">&larr; All apps</a>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mt-8 mb-12">
        <img src="/apps/roomcalc-icon.png" alt="RoomCalc icon" width="128" height="128" class="rounded-[28px] shadow-lg" />
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-3"><span class="gradient-text">RoomCalc</span></h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-text-muted">Construction Material Estimator</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Screenshots -->
      <div class="mb-12 overflow-x-auto">
        <div class="flex gap-4 pb-4" style="min-width: max-content;">
          <img src="/apps/roomcalc/screenshots/en/screenshot_1.png" alt="Calculator list" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/roomcalc/screenshots/en/screenshot_2.png" alt="Paint calculator" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/roomcalc/screenshots/en/screenshot_3.png" alt="Wallpaper calculator" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/roomcalc/screenshots/en/screenshot_4.png" alt="Floor calculator" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/roomcalc/screenshots/en/screenshot_5.png" alt="Results" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/roomcalc/screenshots/en/screenshot_6.png" alt="Dark mode" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/apps/roomcalc/screenshots/en/screenshot_7.png" alt="Settings" class="h-[500px] rounded-2xl shadow-lg" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Standing in the store, staring at tiles, wondering how many boxes to buy? RoomCalc gives you the answer in seconds. Free. No subscription. No ads. Ever.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          RoomCalc is a construction material calculator built for homeowners, DIYers, and anyone doing renovation. Eight specialized calculators, a built-in shopping list, and a unit converter — everything you need from planning to checkout.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">8 Calculators</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-text-muted mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">2D Floor Plan</strong> — see your room as a blueprint with doors, windows, and dimension arrows. Makes abstract numbers visual</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Tile Calculator</strong> — enter room size and tile dimensions, get exact quantity with waste included</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Paint Calculator</strong> — wall dimensions, coats, coverage rate. Exact gallons or liters</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Wallpaper Calculator</strong> — perimeter, height, roll size, pattern repeat. Deducts windows and doors</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Flooring, Concrete, Drywall</strong> — plus area calculator and unit converter</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Smart Shopping List</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Every calculation result can be sent to your shopping list with one tap. Check items off as you buy them. Add custom items manually. Share with your partner or contractor. Built-in price summary.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Why RoomCalc?</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-text-muted">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">100% Free</strong> — no subscription, no in-app purchases, no hidden costs</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Zero Ads</strong> — not now, not ever</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Works Offline</strong> — calculate on the job site with no signal</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Material Reference Guide</strong> — paint coverage, tile sizes, concrete bag yields. No need to Google</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Dark & Light Mode</strong> — looks great in bright sunlight or in a dim basement</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Coming to App Store</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted">RoomCalc is preparing for release. Free for iOS.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-3">All data stays on your device. Nothing is collected, tracked, or sent anywhere.</p>
        <a href="/apps/roomcalc/privacy" class="text-sm text-accent-purple hover:underline">Privacy Policy &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">
        <p>Questions or feedback: <a href="mailto:magic4e@gmail.com" class="text-accent-purple hover:underline">magic4e@gmail.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
